author: rhuijben
msg: Fix a few small issues in the dump_editor of svnrdump.
(make_dir_baton): Use svn_uri_join() as fs paths are no dirents and a
_many() variant is not necessecary for two components. Don't strdup "/"
(apply_textdelta): Use svn_io_open_unique_file3() to avoid mixing utf-8
and non utf-8 paths by using apr and svn_io functions on the same paths.
